head of the Kyohachi School.

00:41.610 --> 00:43.870
<i>He doesn't always have it
 together, but even so...</i>

00:45.710 --> 00:48.070
If you want to learn swordsmanship here,

00:48.070 --> 00:49.390
speak to him.

00:49.750 --> 00:50.940
